g.text: Level 3 Diagram for Searching Staff Profiles
Asks for the data to filter the staff profiles
Sends the data to filter the staff profiles
The data can be First Name and/or Last Name and/or Full Name
throw BusinessRuleValidationException("Specialization with this name not found.")
This will return a queryable list of all staff profiles.
This means that other queries can be chained
to this one in order to filter the staff profiles.
Returns the queryable list of all staff profiles
Returns the queryable list of staff profiles filtered by First Name
Returns the queryable list of staff profiles filtered by Last Name
Returns the queryable list of staff profiles filtered by Full Name
Returns the queryable list of staff profiles filtered by Email
Returns the queryable list of staff profiles filtered by SpecializationId
